    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/19ed1df4d8a9c6a7f30f1715f1631301.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=135 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/9cebcbd65bdd79760af66fd887f7e83e.poster.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/9cebcbd65bdd79760af66fd887f7e83e.webm?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/9cebcbd65bdd79760af66fd887f7e83e.mp4?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Keep Leapin' ! </strong>You play as <strong>Harry</strong>, who's &quot;oddly shaped&quot;, orange and most importantly - <strong>very bouncy!</strong> Experience the fine line between maddening challenge and irresistible fun. Just as fun to blitz through at top speed as it is to enjoy casually while tuning into your favorite podcast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/2bf4b9bffc0c3abcc937abd59bf4798b.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=135 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/dca6bc36cd779ba3a79233317b2ad70c.poster.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/dca6bc36cd779ba3a79233317b2ad70c.webm?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/dca6bc36cd779ba3a79233317b2ad70c.mp4?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of fast-paced arcade gameplay grounded in physics. Every bounce, boost and collision is handled dynamicly, adding depth and challenge to every move. It’s the perfect combination of skill, strategy, and pure fun (and a sprinkle of rage).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/8440a70dc333f59ddfc88e32d6381d33.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=135 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/4751ef84338615f7146aa74715183edd.poster.avif?t=1754948575\" width=798 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/4751ef84338615f7146aa74715183edd.webm?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/4751ef84338615f7146aa74715183edd.mp4?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place in a single level that consists of 100 segments. Loose yourself in the satisfying movement which features numerous traversal options!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/93aea0aec2017dc3420f7edafa52faa1.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=135 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/19472014be8422053e9b0678593c0ac0.poster.avif?t=1754948575\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/19472014be8422053e9b0678593c0ac0.webm?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069030/extras/19472014be8422053e9b0678593c0ac0.mp4?t=1754948575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry about smacking Harry into things — it’s all part of the fun. The unique movement system might test your patience at first, but instant restarts keep the action flowing. What starts as frustration soon transforms into mastery, as bouncing, dashing, and flipping become second nature. Before long, the levels turn into your personal playground, and the rage is replaced by the pure satisfaction of movement.</p>",
